{"tid":2145432,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[HDD] 換 2TB Hard Disk 一問","createTime":"2020-08-08T05:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T05:53:40.000Z","uid":362393,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec427f321ac18006c8d37a24213881d0257ef6c","tid":2145432,"uid":362393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>唔撚好同我講換 SSD 我係窮JJ</strong></span></span> <br />\n(同埋我本身都有條 M.2)<br />\n<br />\n依家我用緊 TOSHIBA 既 2TB Hard Disk (DT01ACA200)<br />\n用左大約 40000 個鐘之後開始出現壞 sector<br />\n<br />\n因為我冇 backup drive, 想要盡快買個新既<br />\n想知依家買邊隻 hard disk 最抵最耐用?<br />\n<br />\n本身想買 Seagate barracuda pro 2TB, 不過香港好似冇行貨買<br />\nSeagate 好似得 Ironwolf Pro 2TB 同 Barracuda 2TB<br />\n所以依家唔知點算, 會唔會買返同款 TOSHIBA 好d?<br />\n<br />\n我要既要求唔多, 最好係 7200rpm, 2TB + 32-bit OS compatible<br />\n有冇巴絲有好推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a158225fcab6a9afec461ccc624f6e68b5725ca7","tid":2145432,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"32 bit OS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7827888dc2f5e841b5cba736b9ff4405bceb5c47","tid":2145432,"uid":58345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"TOSHIBA DT01ACA300"},{"pid":"e237b482cfb461c76d1cba462b457490d178742a","tid":2145432,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"WD己自爆咩HDD用SMR<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996158</a>"},{"pid":"bb4948ee8635dfe95ec723a32d7f86dc1a190999","tid":2145432,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"2tb 3tb都多伏<br />\n一係1tb wd 仲要睇code<br />\n一係4tb企業級"},{"pid":"ed7a385e8d6d48364f3e707a2da03c55d19e437d","tid":2145432,"uid":362393,"like":0,"dislike"